{"tid":2358790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支持特朗普遭連座 撐港參議員霍利新書出版被腰斬","createTime":"2021-01-08T11:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:52:00.000Z","uid":75656,"like":9,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"218dafa62b543a400551ad7395e0bc5502852de5","tid":2358790,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:24:46.000Z","msg":"在發生特朗普支持者衝擊國會大樓後，不但特朗普遭社交媒體禁制在網上發聲，支持特朗普推翻選舉結果的人亦受牽連。美國五大出版商之一的Simon &amp; Schuster周四宣佈，取消出版參議員霍利（Josh Hawley）原定於6月面世的新書《The Tyranny of Big Tech》。霍利回應指書商侵犯了第一修正案。<br />\n<br />\nSimon &amp; Schuster在聲明中表示，這個是艱難決定，「作為出版商，擴大不同聲音和觀點永遠是我們的使命。但與此同時，我們需要認真處理我們作為公民肩付的更大公共責任。基於霍利議員在危險威脅中所扮演的角色，我們不能再支持他。」<br />\n<br />\n霍利在Twitter回應表示，禁制他的書是「奧威爾式」（Orwellian，小說《1984》中的橋段，形容極權）做法。他指責Simon &amp; Schuster取消他的新書出版合約，只因為他代表他的選民，在國會中提出選舉公正的辯論，而這做法被Simon &amp; Schuster定義為煽動。<br />\n<br />\n霍利補充表示，會將Simon &amp; Schuster告上法庭。不過，Simon &amp; Schuster表示有信心他們的做法未有違反合約。<br />\n<br />\n霍利的新書已在亞馬遜（Amazon）和其他網上零售商預售，但Simon &amp; Schuster宣佈取消出版後，亞馬遜已將預售下架。新書主題與選舉或特朗普無關，反而涉及科企如Google、FACEBOOK和亞馬遜。目前未清楚Simon &amp; Schuster會否退還或是沒收出書費用，霍利也未曾交代會否另找出版商，還是自行出版新作。<br />\n<br />\n這次取消出版亦引發公眾質疑，出版商日後會否封殺所有特朗普盟友。曾於去年秋季為另一名支持特朗普推翻選舉結果的參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）出書的保守派出版商Regnery未有感受到壓力。總裁史賓斯（Tom Spence）表示，暫時與克魯茲未有新的出版合約，但樂意再次合作，亦歡迎霍利將新書交由他們出版。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210108/JFOU3FFY3NA4ZNF3JBLIGF6R7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210108%2FJFOU3FFY3NA4ZNF3JBLIGF6R7U%2F&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTISEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=7f6a06c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210108%2FJFOU3FFY3NA4ZNF3JBLIGF6R7U%2F&h=6760a072\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210108/JFOU3FFY3NA4ZNF3JBLIGF6R7U/</a>"},{"pid":"d871b996f9605e3cf63c0f2aa08b812f823bd2fa","tid":2358790,"uid":254165,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:25:31.000Z","msg":"左膠：美國好民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b23e1178cf65024e8623ac5cc55ec4f22f9638","tid":2358790,"uid":134474,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:25:47.000Z","msg":"男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78c0a0bcf8ee6f1a530c09080a330513bd55d53","tid":2358790,"uid":78470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:27:11.000Z","msg":"等兒登做總統就即刻拉侵同埋反對既議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d18385405abc8a4f0032ae27476719e0c6e2b5","tid":2358790,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"兩黨<span class=\"red\">共</span>識"},{"pid":"ee5fadf1e59531039bca651045b261dc0a18bee8","tid":2358790,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"更重要因為本書叫《The Tyranny of Big Tech》<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5925f6aa679694b3d9a072fa3dd17db6e37a5f20","tid":2358790,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee5fadf1e59531039bca651045b261dc0a18bee8","tid":2358790,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"更重要因為本書叫《The Tyranny of Big Tech》<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:30:11.000Z","msg":"Suckerb又贏"},{"pid":"0b0c9f3fd851c655211358d4cb22840a3825ecaa","tid":2358790,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:30:17.000Z","msg":"唔睇清楚仲以為Hawley寫左本我的奮鬥美國版"},{"pid":"80c1d7fa2838abdab8d3e3ae73a5c4f1336ee180","tid":2358790,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870963a968859a746212cebbefe380058e991d1f","tid":2358790,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislik